casebody.data:
Sayre, Respondent, v. Hutkopf, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, Trial Term. April 30, 1891.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bischoff, JJ.

D. Leventritt, for appellant. G. Parr, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, with costs to appellant, and new trial ordered.
